{"tid":524850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王宗堯拍片　籲勿做補選苦主","createTime":"2018-01-10T04:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T05:26:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"310ef8ff1bb94f928081b361a1525669c9d28c9f","tid":524850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180110/20270094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F20270094&d=jv5VVIV7ClBSI%2BGCvZSj9W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=990e56fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F20270094&h=d0ad005f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180110/20270094</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：王宗堯拍片　籲勿做補選苦主 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n      <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180110/large/a1107a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180110%2Flarge%2Fa1107a.gif&h=ab047565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n唔少人都知道3.11有立法會補選，但嚟緊嘅星期日係民主派新東同九西初選日，則未必咁多人知嘞！參加咗九西初選嘅前議員姚松炎為咗催谷初選投票率，亦搞搞新意思，搵嚟男神王宗堯拍片（圖），話畀大家聽初選幾咁重要。<br />\n<br />\n片中嘅王宗堯1月10日出發到南非，話3.11前會返港，準備喺補選投票支持姚松炎，點知原來姚松炎喺初選出局，令專登返港投票嘅佢後悔莫及，成為3.11另類苦主。片入面公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊就話嘞，唔少人只知有補選而不知有初選，為免3.11投唔到姚教授，首要係1.14初選投票令佢出線，而姚教授組織嘅「山旮旯投票團」當日會帶支持者出動投票，呼籲大家留意周日投票詳情。"},{"pid":"09aebdae9642d001dc8676e652efaeb150fc51ce","tid":524850,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持關ching 補選投白票"},{"pid":"45da7928900217ebbf7f1590b2519e75721e7fbb","tid":524850,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:12:59.000Z","msg":"結果都係改變唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554f499efe764a5a30ae50d22a3b809c688de532","tid":524850,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"反而擔心港共會再DQ人<br />\n咁九西得返基哥上"}]}